# Copy to .env and fill in. These are the SAME public values the web app uses
# (VITE_SUPABASE_URL / VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY). The anon key is safe to ship in a
# mobile binary: every table is gated by Row Level Security and every edge
# function does its own auth. NEVER put the service_role key here.
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
